ed another player using LIFESPARK in the last month, and banned players who had not earned the required Divine Gems legitimately. Sweeps covering other 4* Titans, Prestige levels, Boost Relics and 5* Relics are currently in progress.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, please be aware that using any exploit to collect event rewards multiple times results in a permanent ban.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>DOT CONTENT CREATORS:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Whilst you wait for the Livestream\u2019s return, go check out some of the great DoT content creators and streamers across YouTube! Click the link on their names to go to their channels, and <strong>hit that subscribe button<\/strong> to get their latest videos as they drop:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UC5S1d6IYSrt95MLKy4ITmMQ\/featured\">F2P Zeus<\/a> &#8211; reactions, updates, battles, player profiles, Titan and Relic reviews.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCJ9s6BIyM7uUPJVAk7nbonw\">Vintage Plays<\/a> &#8211; DoT community conversations, overviews and streams.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/TheMonkeygrl\">Dee NTG<\/a> &#8211; Insights from long-time player of DoT and leader of NTG.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCTJ9Ysb6tbhvbCOoTungXxQ\/videos\">Ron Gamer<\/a> &#8211; Tips and Titan showcases.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/zalonisap\">ZALON<\/a> &#8211; Streams, discussions, roundtables, interactive playthroughs.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCbYtgn5sKNLnYiIAF_DEspQ\">Godan<\/a> &#8211; Titan showcases, player showcases, games updates, opinions.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCFrgkLKVG3R48foLzs_c5GA\">Gason86<\/a> &#8211; Titan vs Titan content, event overviews.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/mwhutchins\">Prometheo NTG<\/a> &#8211; Titan and Troop meta analysis.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.